Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.27,0:00:18.74,Lyrics EN,,0,0,0,,Even though it hurts…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.74,0:00:21.95,Lyrics EN,,0,0,0,,…even though I feel sad…
